{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "八千代（盔甲Ver.） 第3话 祖父的心意",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（我是为了什么\\n才要变强呢……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（我一直在追求最强，\\n变强就是为了成为最强。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（但是……要说成为\\n最强之后的事……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（我不擅长思考复杂的事……\\n唔唔唔……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "……\\n想不明白！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "呀啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "嗯？山茶花？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "抱歉，我被你的叫声\\n吓到了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "啊，抱歉。\\n我刚才在想一些事情。\\n你找我有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "是的，你还记得那个\\n从骸众手上救下的女孩吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "她和她家人写来了信，\\n说想表达对我们救了她的谢意。\\n我就想问问你要不要一起去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "真的吗！？当然了！\\n我也去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "家康不一起吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "是的，家康大人要和\\n阿尔贝里亚王室的诸位会谈，\\n便写了致歉函托我捎去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "上面的人好忙啊。\\n但忙成这样还能把武艺\\n练得那么好，只能说佩服了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "我听说你祖父也是\\n公务练武两不误哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "山茶花，你能给我讲讲\\n我祖父在幕府时的事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "其实我不太了解\\n他作为幕府官员的一面。\\n因为他都不提及城里的事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "其实我也只见过他几次，\\n你要是不介意，\\n可以给你讲讲我听过的传闻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "据说你祖父\\n身为将军家的剑术指导，\\n深得将军信赖。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "因此他还受命指导\\n十二龙氏的剑术，家康大人他们\\n也曾受过你祖父的指点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "家康也从祖父那里\\n学过剑啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "但是，指导剑术的人为什么\\n会被委任守护那石头啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "契机好像是\\n你祖父的口头禅哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "口头禅……难道是指\\n“要成为最强的剑士”？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "是的。你祖父言出必行，\\n即使担任要职以后\\n也没有松懈，一直坚持锻炼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "一定是他的勤勉性格\\n得到了信赖，才会被选为\\n“道反石”的守护者吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "原来我那个祖父在人前\\n是个性格认真的人啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "呵呵，觉得很意外吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "嗯。我第一次听说他是\\n幕府官员的时候还以为是吹牛呢。\\n毕竟他在家很豪放嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "这一点\\n看你就能想象得出。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "对吧？我的性格\\n就是遗传自他。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "那你是不是也知道……\\n我祖父为什么会离开幕府？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "他来辞行的时候，我记得\\n他说是“为了保护家人”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "应该正好是他被任命为\\n“道反石”守护者那会儿……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代的祖父",
            "context": "决定保护那石头，\\n就意味着可能会给家人\\n带来危险。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代的祖父",
            "context": "所以今后我想\\n在珍爱的家人身旁\\n守护日出之国的安宁。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "祖父还说过这话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "他深爱着自己的家人呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "听说他之所以想成为幕府官员，\\n本就是为了守护家人\\n赖以生存的日出之国。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "祖父……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（那么，祖父的剑也好，强大也罢，\\n都是为了我们这些家人？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "（但是现在祖父和姐姐都不在了，\\n我又是为了什么才要变强呢……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "八千代，\\n快到村子了哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "那女孩的家……啊，在那边。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "啊……你们是圣城的人……\\n不好意思！你们有看到阿妮……\\n有看到我女儿吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "诶？不，我们没看到啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "我女儿不见了！\\n今天早上还在家的……\\n找遍了村子都不见人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "你说什么！？\\n山茶花！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "嗯，我们分头去找吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "阿妮？\\n你在哪？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "（总觉得心神不宁的……\\n有种不祥的预感……那是！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01",
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众",
            "context": "呵呵……好了，这个诱饵\\n要怎么用呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "呼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "放了那女孩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "啊……是大姐姐……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众",
            "context": "嚯，钓到了亥之从者啊，\\n可惜我要找的不是你，\\n麻烦你把那个女武士带过来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "我拒绝。很遗憾，\\n在我带她来之前……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "我会先收拾掉你。\\n哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众",
            "context": "包袱有点碍事呢……给你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "呀啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "竟然把阿妮扔过来……\\n唔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "唔、嗯……谢谢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众",
            "context": "你还有空管小孩子吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110311_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "山茶花",
            "context": "唔！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "大姐姐！大姐姐！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120211_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "骸众",
            "context": "我就放了你吧。\\n但你可得替我跑一趟腿哦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "好慢……天都黑了，\\n山茶花跑到哪里去了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "阿妮！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "太好了！没事就好……\\n诶？你是一个人回来的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "大姐姐！另一个姐姐她……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿妮",
            "context": "她为了救我，\\n被坏蛋给带走了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110064_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八千代",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}